{"tid":1770723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈射入屋燒毀圖書，圖書館要求市民賠償","createTime":"2019-12-05T11:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T12:01:14.000Z","uid":53000,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be5655a39c06ee5494094f44e2f8de93ecda91db","tid":1770723,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T11:00:00.000Z","msg":"【大城小事】催淚彈射入屋圖書被毀　圖書館要求賠錢　作者知悉主動贈書補償<br />\n<br />\n上月中，理大圍城之際，警方驅散聲援群眾，曾於佐敦柯士甸道一帶施放多枚催淚彈，甚至射爆唐樓玻璃，導致單位起火。<br />\n<br />\n火，是撲熄了，但事未完。<br />\n<br />\n書本原是公共圖書館借閱的藏品，但受到催淚彈波及被毀，無法完好退還。郭小姐的女兒親自到圖書館解釋事件，但職員沒有理會，僅重申「凡有損毀、損失都要借閲讀者賠償」。三本燒焦的圖書，要她們合共賠上超過 200 港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B-%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%84%E5%85%A5%E5%B1%8B%E5%9C%96%E6%9B%B8%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%80-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%B4%88%E6%9B%B8%E8%A3%9C%E5%84%9F-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB-%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E%E7%94%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2582%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25B4%2588%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2584%259F-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E8%258B%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%2594%259C%2F&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=4338ee94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2582%2589%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%